      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# === Celda 2: Importar librerías y comprobar versiones ===\n",
        "import cudf\n",
        "import cugraph\n",
        "import networkx as nx\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"cuDF versión:\", cudf.__version__)\n",
        "print(\"cuGraph versión:\", cugraph.__version__)\n",
        "print(\"NetworkX versión:\", nx.__version__)\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "Zv-W21STIrYp",
        "outputId": "d3ed3e62-0720-489e-e295-2f3d50a6c9d0"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "cuDF versión: 25.04.00\n",
            "cuGraph versión: 25.04.01\n",
            "NetworkX versión: 3.5\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# === Celda 3: Generar grafo Watts–Strogatz y dataset de aristas\n",
        "n = 100        # número de nodos\n",
        "k = 4          # vecinos en el anillo\n",
        "p = 0.1        # probabilidad de rewiring\n",
        "seed = 42\n",
        "\n",
        "# Generar con NetworkX\n",
        "G_nx = nx.watts_strogatz_graph(n=n, k=k, p=p, seed=seed)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Crear DataFrame de aristas (peso uniforme = 1.0)\n",
        "edges = [(u, v, 1.0) for u, v in G_nx.edges()]\n",
        "cu_edges = cudf.DataFrame(edges, columns=['src', 'dst', 'weight'])\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "cxmPw0ihJ0fd"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# === Celda 4: Construir el grafo en cuGraph ===\n",
        "G_cu = cugraph.Graph(directed=False)\n",
        "G_cu.from_cudf_edgelist(\n",
        "    cu_edges,\n",
        "    source='src',\n",
        "    destination='dst',\n",
        "    edge_attr='weight'\n",
        ")\n",
        "print(f\"Nodos en cuGraph: {G_cu.number_of_vertices()}, Aristas: {G_cu.number_of_edges()}\")\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "LTgZtrE3K8DO",
        "outputId": "3b5175e5-8a82-4976-de2c-e6a0b17b48d7"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Nodos en cuGraph: 100, Aristas: 0\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# === Celda 5: Ejecutar algoritmos en GPU ===\n",
        "# 5.1 PageRank\n",
        "pr_df = cugraph.pagerank(G_cu)\n",
        "\n",
        "# 5.2 SSSP desde el nodo 0\n",
        "sssp_df = cugraph.sssp(G_cu, source=0)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Convertir a pandas/dict para usar en NetworkX\n",
        "pr_dict   = pr_df.to_pandas().set_index('vertex')['pagerank'].to_dict()\n",
        "sssp_dict = sssp_df.to_pandas().set_index('vertex')['distance'].to_dict()\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "znE7NlsrLI5P",
        "outputId": "0bab6fb6-dbf6-4fa1-948f-f2a04dcb871e"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stderr",
          "text": [
            "/usr/local/lib/python3.11/dist-packages/cugraph/link_analysis/pagerank.py:232: UserWarning: Pagerank expects the 'store_transposed' flag to be set to 'True' for optimal performance during the graph creation\n",
            "  warnings.warn(warning_msg, UserWarning)\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# === Celda 6: Visualizar en NetworkX  Matplotlib\n",
        "# Asignar atributos a G_nx\n",
        "nx.set_node_attributes(G_nx, pr_dict,   name='pagerank')\n",
        "nx.set_node_attributes(G_nx, sssp_dict, name='distance')\n",
        "\n",
        "# Tamaño de nodo ∝ PageRank\n",
        "node_sizes = [5000 * G_nx.nodes[v]['pagerank'] for v in G_nx]\n",
        "\n",
        "# Posiciones con spring layout\n",
        "pos = nx.spring_layout(G_nx, seed=seed)\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(8, 6))\n",
        "nx.draw_networkx_edges(G_nx, pos, alpha=0.3)\n",
        "nodes = nx.draw_networkx_nodes(\n",
        "    G_nx, pos,\n",
        "    node_size=node_sizes,\n",
        "    cmap=plt.cm.viridis,\n",
        "    node_color=[G_nx.nodes[v]['distance'] for v in G_nx],\n",
        ")\n",
        "plt.colorbar(nodes, label='Distancia desde nodo 0')\n",
        "plt.title('Watts–Strogatz: tamaño ~ PageRank, color ~ SSSP')\n",
        "plt.axis('off')\n",
        "plt.show()\n"
      ],
